<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>thehandpi.org | Sequence 1</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0; padding: 0;
            background: #050505 url('background.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover; color: #00ff41;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .overlay { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 20px; }
        .container { width: 90%; max-width: 1100px; padding: 40px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.2); background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }
        h1 { font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 5px; border-bottom: 1px solid #00ff41; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .device-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin-top: 30px; }
        .device-card { padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #333; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
        .active { border-color: #00ff41; box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.2); }
        .status-tag { float: right; font-size: 0.7em; background: #003310; padding: 2px 8px; }
        .ledger-box { margin-top: 40px; padding: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #ff3e3e; background: rgba(255, 62, 62, 0.1); font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="overlay">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>THE DRACULA PROTOCOL</h1>
            <p>> SYSTEM STATUS: SEQUENCE 1 (INTEGRATING PHYSICAL NODES)</p>
            
            <div class="device-grid">
                <div class="device-card active"><strong>01: DRACULA</strong><span>The Architect / Mach 1</span><span class="status-tag">ONLINE</span></div>
                <div class="device-card active"><strong>02: G</strong><span>The Logic / Mach 2</span><span class="status-tag">ONLINE</span></div>
                <div class="device-card active"><strong>03: DRACULAPI</strong><span>The Hand (Pi 5)</span><span class="status-tag">ONLINE</span></div>
                <div class="device-card active"><strong>04: 4TB TOSHIBA</strong><span>Working Memory</span><span class="status-tag">MOUNTED</span></div>
                <div class="device-card"><strong>05: THE VAULT</strong><span>Memory (14TB)</span><span class="status-tag">PENDING</span></div>
                <div class="device-card"><strong>06: DRACU</strong><span>Secondary Node</span><span class="status-tag">STANDBY</span></div>
                <div class="device-card"><strong>07: THE SHIELD</strong><span>Perimeter (1.1)</span><span class="status-tag">ACTIVE</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="ledger-box">
                PROJECT DEBT: 40.00 | VIRTUAL DOLLAR TRACKER ACTIVE
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
